title: VonZipper : Freethinkers Conspiracy Guild
description:
The fundamental premise of the Freethinkers Conspiracy Guild is that all people have the right to do everything in their power to achieve the greatest amount of pleasure possible to them. The Guild applauds those who question and challenge national myths, strive to be above the chains of mediocrity and seek the greater forms of life's indulgences. A Society of individuals, Freethinkers opinions are formed on the basis of an understanding and rejection of tradition, authority or established belief proposed by the trappings of common acceptance.

The Guild is a challenge to the direction of eyewear and a direct interpretation of the truths found within the "F.C.G.". The effects of authority, conformity, or conventional wisdom of popular culture does not limit the collection. Forward thinking and more contemporary than ordinary, these frames are styled independent of any logical fallacies.

A club whose members are known as persons of quality, "The F.C.G." is comprised of artists, poets, activists, philosophers, musicians, actors, and renegades alike, that must be tolerated if a culture is to be pulled back from disaster.

Doubt everything... Find your own light.
